    "description": "《Crash Course Builder》是一款紧张刺激的节奏赛车游戏，充满了震碎屏幕的爆炸和滑稽的布娃娃物理效果。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏目的。</h2>系好安全带，做好迎接终极挑战的准备，驾驶你的赛车穿过融化心灵的障碍赛道，而大呼过瘾的你一心只想着再...爽...一次！<br><br>游戏的目的很简单...以任何必要的方式到达终点！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382630/extras/6dafef5213ce13647161e69512297c48.poster.avif?t=1752681921\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382630/extras/6dafef5213ce13647161e69512297c48.webm?t=1752681921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382630/extras/6dafef5213ce13647161e69512297c48.mp4?t=1752681921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >但是,但是，但是...怎样才能做到呢？</h2><br>左右转向，穿过疯狂的障碍赛道。<br>听起来很简单，对吧？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382630/extras/f4957996ac428b0b8fb88134c241a509.poster.avif?t=1752681921\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382630/extras/f4957996ac428b0b8fb88134c241a509.webm?t=1752681921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382630/extras/f4957996ac428b0b8fb88134c241a509.mp4?t=1752681921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >太简单了？</h2><br>&quot;一路过关来到<br> 不可能赛道&quot;（哦啊）<br>最少的检查点，最疯狂的角度。<br>你能打通一条不可能赛道吗？<br><br>小心翼翼<br>路怒症警告！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382630/extras/ae546b547b57aaa257aa9a94ad6b1d4a.poster.avif?t=1752681921\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382630/extras/ae546b547b57aaa257aa9a94ad6b1d4a.webm?t=1752681921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382630/extras/ae546b547b57aaa257aa9a94ad6b1d4a.mp4?t=1752681921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >喜欢创造多过破坏？</h2><br>如果你认为我们的赛道太容易了（噗），你可以使用我们直观的赛道生成器来创建属于你自己的冲撞赛道！<br>定制每一个弯道、转向和爆炸惊喜，然后让你的好友来挑战你创造的赛道！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382630/extras/43487a8f1b7024ac2c805a8b1705df93.poster.avif?t=1752681921\" width=640 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382630/extras/43487a8f1b7024ac2c805a8b1705df93.webm?t=1752681921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382630/extras/43487a8f1b7024ac2c805a8b1705df93.mp4?t=1752681921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382630/extras/752ef2bc66487691751515cdd223a6e4.poster.avif?t=1752681921\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382630/extras/752ef2bc66487691751515cdd223a6e4.webm?t=1752681921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382630/extras/752ef2bc66487691751515cdd223a6e4.mp4?t=1752681921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382630/extras/81eef544a231fde431b6cc99fbc41ada.poster.avif?t=1752681921\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382630/extras/81eef544a231fde431b6cc99fbc41ada.webm?t=1752681921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382630/extras/81eef544a231fde431b6cc99fbc41ada.mp4?t=1752681921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >冲撞俱乐部总部</h2><br>加入在线冲撞俱乐部社区，展示你精心制作的混乱杰作。<br>与来自世界各地的玩家互动，游玩他们的赛道，并对他们的作品进行评分。<br>为无穷的乐趣和激烈的竞争做好准备吧。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382630/extras/79d97fed8932cf931ee121e52431fcc1.poster.avif?t=1752681921\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382630/extras/79d97fed8932cf931ee121e52431fcc1.webm?t=1752681921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382630/extras/79d97fed8932cf931ee121e52431fcc1.mp4?t=1752681921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>简单、困难、禅意或不可能。</i><br><strong>每个碰撞测试假人都能找到适合自己的游玩风格！</strong>",
